description: Returns information about the specified Firewall Manager applications list.

parameters.name: ListId
parameters.description: The ID of the Firewall Manager applications list that you want the details for.

nested_items.name: ListId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Firewall Manager applications list.

nested_items.name: ListName
nested_items.description: The name of the Firewall Manager applications list.

nested_items.name: ListUpdateToken
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for each update to the list. When you update the list, the update token must match the token of the current version of the application list. You can retrieve the update token by getting the list.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The time that the Firewall Manager applications list was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The time that the Firewall Manager applications list was last updated.

nested_items.name: AppsList
nested_items.description: An array of applications in the Firewall Manager applications list.

nested_items.name: Protocol
nested_items.description: The IP protocol name or number. The name can be one of tcp, udp, or icmp. For information on possible numbers, see Protocol Numbers.

nested_items.name: Port
nested_items.description: The application's port number, for example 80.

nested_items.name: PreviousAppsList
nested_items.description: A map of previous version numbers to their corresponding App object arrays.

nested_items.name: Protocol
nested_items.description: The IP protocol name or number. The name can be one of tcp, udp, or icmp. For information on possible numbers, see Protocol Numbers.

nested_items.name: Port
nested_items.description: The application's port number, for example 80.

nested_items.name: AppsListArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the applications list.
